README file for the meta-amg88xx
meta-amg88xx is home for the python libraries needed to read using i2c the data from the amg8833 Adafruit sensor. 
It includes as well recipes for 2 python scripts:
python-captura which captures a frame from the sensor and draws in a 800x800 jpg file a color image from indigo to red being indigo the lowest tempertaure and read the highes temperature read from the sensor. 
python-hotspot which takes a gray scale image and applys a Gaussian filter, binarizes the image, and detects and circles the hotspots. 


